{
  "name": "SlicerItems",
  "summary": "<p>如果切片器基于工作簿中的数据或非 OLAP 外部数据，那么若要访问表示该切片器中项目的 <strong>SlicerItems</strong> 集合，请使用与该切片器关联的 <strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n<p>如果切片器基于 OLAP 数据连接，那么若要访问表示该切片器中项目的 <strong>SlicerItems</strong> 集合，请使用代表层次结构级别的 <strong>SlicerCacheLevel</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上数据透视表第一个切片器的缓存中切片器项的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`切片器项的数量：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sliItems.Count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上名为“切片器_score”的切片器缓存中切片器项的名称逐个赋值到单元格中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_score&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">11</span>, i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示包含�� <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象中的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItem/SlicerItem .htm#SlicerItem.SlicerItem\">SlicerItem</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回集合中对象的数量。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存中切片器项的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItem/SlicerItem .htm#SlicerItem.SlicerItem\">SlicerItem</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第二个切片器缓存中第三个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中活动工作表上数据透视表第一个切片器的缓存中名为“张三”的切片器项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;张三&quot;</span>)\n    sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>SlicerItem</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}